title: prem joshua & chintan - ahir [indian electronica] [1996] VBR mp3
description:
With Ahir, multi-instrumentalists and composers Prem Joshua and Chintan harvest the creative fruits of a 15-year musical partnership. Drawing on material from their recent world tours, the essence of ancient Indian raga music is successfully united with infectious contemporary grooves creating a true masterpiece of fresh and inspired global music.

Label: MedialMusic (Germany)
